0Air%20Force%20to%20a%20new%20aviation%20standard%20%E2%80%94%20Western%20combat%20aviation.%20From%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20war%2C%20we%20have%20been%20talking%20with%20our%20partners%20about%20the%20need%20to%20close%20the%20Ukrainian%20sky%20from%20Russian%20missiles%20and%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ukrainian%20president%20wrote%2C%20thanking%20Denmark%2C%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States%20for%20the%20long-awaited%20aircraft%20that%20are%20now%20%26quot%3Ba%20reality%20in%20our%20sky.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20proud%20of%20all%20our%20guys%20who%20are%20skillfully%20mastering%20these%20aircraft%20and%20have%20already%20started%20using%20them%20for%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20long%20believed%20the%20F-16%20would%20be%20a%20game%20changer%20in%20its%20defensive%20war%20against%20Russia.%20But%20with%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20aircraft%20and%20pilots%20who%20know%20how%20to%20fly%20them%2C%20they%20will%20likely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-may-not-use-f16s-for-frontline-offensives-it-wanted-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebe%20cautious%20to%20avoid%20losses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20means%20they'll%20need%20hefty%20protection%20while%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20fly%20mostly%20in%20Ukrainian%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20threat%20to%20them%20is%20long-range%20Russian%20SAMs%20(S-400s)%20and%20Russian%20fighters%20staying%20inside%20Russian%20air%20space%20but%20launching%20long-range%20air-to-air%20missiles%20into%20Ukrainian%20airspace%2C%26quot%3B%20Peter%20Layton%2C%20a%20fellow%20at%20the%20Griffith%20Asia%20Institute%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US-made%20aircraft%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-american-missiles-can-do-ukraine-f-16s-against-russia-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair-to-air%20missiles%3C