a%20Banerjee%20as%20an%20individual%20and%20has%20professional%20relations%20with%20her%20but%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolitician%20Mamata%20Banerjee%26quot%3B%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20my%20cup%20of%20tea%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20PTI%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Governor%2C%20who%20has%20often%20been%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20Banerjee-led%20Trinamool%20Congress%20Government%2C%20spoke%20candidly%20about%20their%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20relationship%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Bose%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhich%20Mamata%20Banerjee%3F%20There%20are%20three%20Mamata%20Banerjees%20in%20front%20of%20me.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BOne%20is%20the%20individual%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20I%20have%20a%20very%20good%20relationship%20with%20her.%20Second%20is%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20I%20have%20professional%20relations%20with%20her.%20Third%20is%20the%20politician%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20that's%20not%20my%20cup%20of%20tea%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20elections%2C%20she%20mixed%20up%20the%20issues.%20The%20chief%20minister%20merged%20with%20the%20politician%2C%20made%20certain%20statements.%20I%20also%20became%20an%20individual%2C%20not%20the%20governor.%20I%20sued%20her%20for%20damages%2C%20for%20defamation.%20That%20is%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOtherwise%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20my%20friend.%20The%20chief%20minister%20is%20my%20colleague%20and%20I%20am%20not%20a%20politician%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPoliticians%20play%20certain%20roles%20in%20their%20own%20way.%20I%20won't%20allow%20that%20to%20interfere%20with%20my%20self-respect.%20There%20the%20relationship%20stands%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20were%20made%20against%20the%20governor%20by%20a%20contractual%20employee%20of%20Raj%20Bhavan.%20An%20in-house%20preliminary%20inquiry%20report%20by%20a%20Raj%20Bhavan%20panel%20has%20dismissed%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20attacks%20by%20Banerjee%20and%20TMC%20leaders%20over%20the%20charges%2C%20Bose%20had%20moved%20a%20defamation%20suit%20against%20Banerjee%20and%20some%20other%20TMC%20leaders%2C%20following%20which%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20restrained%20them%20from%20making%20any%20defamatory%20or%20incorrect%20statement%20against%20the%20Governor%20in%20an%20interim%20order%20till%20August%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20moving%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20Governor%20for%20allegedly%20withholding%20assent%20on%20eight%20bills%2C%20he%20said%20there%20are%20no%20bills%20pending%20with%20his%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20go%20into%20the%20lighter%20vein%2C%20only%20bill%20which%20is%20pending%20in%20the%20Bengal%20Raj%20Bhavan%20are%20the%20fuel%20bills.%20No%20bill%20of%20the%20government%20which%20is%20sent%20by%20the%20Assembly%20is%20pending%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20case%20that%20eight%20bills%20are%20pending%20with%20the%20Governor.%20Six%20bills%20have%20been%20reserved%20for%20the%20President.%20One%20bill%20is%20kept%20for%20discussion%20with%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20Government%20on%20certain%20clarifications%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20they%20come%20for%20clarification%2C%20those%20bills%20will%20be%20cleared%20or%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20this%20way%20or%20that%20way.%20One%20bill%20is%20sub-judice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOtherwise%2C%20there%20is%20no%20bill%20passed%20by%20the%20Assembly%20among%20the%20eight%20bills%20that%20they%20have%20pointed%20out%20pending%20with%20the%20Governor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governor%2C%20who%20has%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20White%20Paper%20on%20the%20state's%20finances%2C%20alleged%20that%20financial%20management%20in%20the%20state%20is%20%26quot%3Btardy%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20depending%20on%20the%20white%20paper%20he%20will%20make%20up%20his%20mind%20about%20taking%20%26quot%3Baction%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20many%20respects%2C%20financial%20management%20is%20very%20tardy%2C%20very%20poor%20and%20lopsided%20in%20Bengal.%20I%20could%20also%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%2C%20in%20many%20respects%2C%20the%20budget%20or%20the%20finance%20is%20seeing%20a%20breakdown%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20meltdown%2C%20rather%2C%20if%20I%20may%20say%20so%2C%20in%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20instead%20of%20imposing%20my%20views%20on%20the%20government%2C%20I%20asked%20them%20to%20give%20a%20White%20Paper%2C%20their%20own%20assessment%20of%20the%20factual%20situation%20in%20the%20field.%20The%20White%20Paper%20will%20enable%20them%20to%20have%20a%20reality%20check%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it's%20his%20constitutional%20duty%20to%20uphold%20the%20Constitution%20and%20ensure%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20people%20of%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20that%20is%20not%20there%2C%20action%20has%20to%20be%20taken.%20What%20is%20the%20action%20that%20can%20be%20taken%3F%20It%20is%20also%20spelt%20out%20very%20clearly%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20I%20have%20not%20made%20up%20my%20mind%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20make%20up%20my%20mind%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20White%20Paper.%20Whenever%20it%20comes%2C%20I%20am%20willing%20to%20wait.%20Because%20my%20intention%20is%20to%20correct%2C%20not%20to%20accuse%20anybody%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20kind%20of%20action%20may%20be%20taken%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20lays%20down%20clearly.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20