lding%20displaying%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3BLong%20Live%20Pakistan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20takes%20a%20twist%20when%20the%20group%20of%20people%20enter%20the%20apartment%20belonging%20to%20the%20person%20who%20is%20suspected%20to%20have%20attached%20these%20posters.%20The%20apartment%20appears%20fairly%20small%2C%20dimly%20lit%20with%20just%20utensils%20and%20old%20rusty%20furniture%20lying%20around%20the%20corner.%20They%20then%20enter%20a%20dark%20room%20with%20little%20to%20no%20visibility%20to%20find%20an%20old%20man%20sitting%20on%20the%20floor%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20room%20with%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20alcoholic%20beverage%20in%20his%20hand.%20The%20man%20can%20only%20be%20seen%20when%20some%20people%20turn%20on%20their%20mobile%20flashlights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20then%20begins%20to%20interrogate%20the%20person%20and%20asks%20him%20why%20he%20is%20doing%20such%20things%20while%20staying%20in%20India%20while%20the%20others%20accompanying%20him%20are%20heard%20saying%20this%20man%20looks%20mentally%20ill%20and%20things%20like%20%26quot%3Btujhe%20Pakistan%20jaana%20hain%20toh%20Pakistan%20jaa%26quot%3B%20(If%20you%20want%20to%20go%20to%20Pakistan%20then%20go%20there)%20while%20shouting%20at%20the%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20one%20person%20will%20ask%20a%20question%20at%20a%20time%2C%20I%20will%20not%20answer%20anything%20like%20this%26quot%3B%2C%20says%20the%20individual%20being%20questioned.%20He%20appears%20to%20be%20in%20an%20inebriated%20condition.%20When%20one%20does%20as%20he%20says%20and%20asks%20him%20why%20he%20is%20doing%20such%20things%20he%20replies%2C%20%26quot%3Bmeri%20mohabbat%20hain%20Pakistan%20se%26quot%3B%20(It%20is%20my%20love%20for%20Pakistan).%20The%20individual%20then%20continues%20to%20say%20why%20everyone%20is%20asking%20questions%20even%20when%20only%20one%20person%20is%20heard%20asking%20and%20is%20told%20not%20to%20do%20such%20things%20while%20staying%20in%20Indi