0next%20number%20may%20be%20the%20endowments%20of%20Sikhs%20and%20Christians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20the%20first%20Waqf%20Act%20was%20passed%20in%201954%20and%20the%20first%20amendment%20in%201995%20and%20then%20in%202013%2C%20sources%20said%20now%20Muslim%20women%20and%20common%20Muslims%20%26quot%3Bare%20asking%20why%20the%20government%20is%20not%20changing%20present%20Waqf%20Act%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20land%20goes%20to%20Waqf%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20reversed%2C%20sources%20said.%20This%20is%20why%20powerful%20Muslims%20have%20captured%20Waqf%20board.%20%26quot%3BThe%20women%20and%20children%20are%20suffering.%20If%20a%20Muslim%20woman%20is%20divorced%20then%20she%20and%20her%20children%20will%20not%20get%20any%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20amendment%20has%20two%20key%20parts%20--%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20provision%20for%20inclusion%20of%20women%20in%20Waqf%20boards%3B%20and%20ensuring%20that%20the%20land%20is%20verified%20before%20it%20is%20announced%20as%20Waqf%20property.%20Sources%20said%20it%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20decided%20when%20it%20would%20be%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722789180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fum6j1rso_new-parliament-building_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-law-change-to-help-women-say-sources-warn-of-dangerous-narrative-6263028%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20allegations%20that%20revision%20of%20the%20Waqf%20laws%20is%20a%20ploy%20of%20the%20government%20to%20usurp%20Waqf%20land%2C%20is%20completely%20wrong%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20today%20after%20certain%20remarks%20from%20the%20Muslim%20Law%20Board.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-law-change-to-help-women-say-sources-warn-of-dangerous-narrative-6263028%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3