%20president%2C%20made%20the%20thinly%20veiled%20threat%20in%20a%20post%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmedvedev_telegram%2F520%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelegram%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%2C%20of%20course%2C%20for%20Russia's%20traitors%20to%20rot%20in%20a%20penitentiary%20or%20die%20in%20prison%2C%20as%20has%20often%20happened.%20But%20it%20is%20more%20useful%20to%20get%20out%20our%20own%20people%2C%20who%20worked%20for%20the%20country%2C%20for%20the%20Fatherland%2C%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20the%20traitors%20now%20feverishly%20adopt%20new%20names%20and%20actively%20disguise%20themselves%20under%20the%20witness%20protection%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20follow-up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmedvedev_telegram%2F521%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Medvedev%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BLet%20them%20keep%20on%20barking%2C%20dreaming%20of%20tearing%20apart%20the%20body%20of%20our%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20them%20not%20forget%20about%20the%20perishability%20of%20their%20existence%20in%20this%20world.%20Let%20them%20burn%20in%20hell!%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20released%20by%20Russia%20were%20Vladimir%20Kara-Murza%2C%20a%20Pulitzer%20Prize-winning%20writer%20who%20was%20serving%2025%20years%20on%20a%20treason%20conviction%3B%20opposition%20activist%20Ilya%20Yashin%2C%20imprisoned%20for%20his%20criticism%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%3B%20and%20Oleg%20Orlov%2C%20a%20human%20rights%20campaigner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-of-people-putin-is-suspected-of-assassinating-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistory%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20attempting%20to%20take%20out%20critics%20and%20defectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Russian%20President%20in%202010%