%2C%20the%20Western%20combat%20aviation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20citing%20hundreds%20of%20meetings%20and%20unrelenting%20diplomacy%20to%20obtain%20the%20F-16s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20often%20heard%20'it%20is%20impossible'%20as%20an%20answer%20but%20we%20still%20made%20our%20ambition%2C%20our%20defensive%20need%2C%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20unclear%20what%20missiles%20the%20jets%20are%20equipped%20with.%20A%20longer%20range%20of%20missile%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20have%20a%20greater%20battlefield%20impact%2C%20military%20analysts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20said%20he%20also%20hoped%20to%20lobby%20allied%20neighbouring%20countries%20to%20help%20intercept%20Russian%20missiles%20being%20launched%20at%20Ukraine%20through%20conversations%20at%20the%20Ukraine-NATO%20Council%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20another%20tool%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20try%20it%2C%20so%20that%20NATO%20countries%20can%20talk%20to%20Ukraine%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20small%20coalition%20of%20neighbouring%20countries%20shooting%20down%20enemy%20missiles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20decision%20is%20probably%20difficult%20for%20our%20partners%2C%20they%20are%20always%20afraid%20of%20excessive%20escalation%20but%20we%20are%20fighting%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722786540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fq99mffu8_zelenskiy-fighter-jet_625x300_04_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-f-16-fighter-jets-arrive-in-ukraine-zelensky-says-we-did-it-6262746%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20pilots%20have%20started%20flying%20F-16s%20for%20operations%20within%20the%20nat