heritance%2C%20but%20what%20a%20windfall.%20I%20love%20that%20you%20want%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20the%20money%20while%20still%20doing%20what%20you%20love%20with%20it.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20with%20%2425%2C000%2C%20you%20can%20have%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20look%20at%20ways%20you%20can%20stretch%20your%20dollars.%20To%20help%20you%20toward%20this%20goal%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20Justin%20Rush%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fcfp%5C%22%3Ecertified%20financial%20planner%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20specializes%20in%20tailoring%20his%20clients'%20financial%20plans%20to%20their%20unique%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%5C%22%3Einvesting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rush%20says%20everything%20comes%20down%20to%20personal%20circumstances%20and%20preferences%2C%20but%20he%20offered%20a%20few%20considerations%20to%20help%20you%20design%20your%20situation%20to%20your%20ideal%20specifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERush%20says%20that%20the%20amount%20of%20your%20windfall%20you%20should%20designate%20for%20paying%20off%20bills%20will%20largely%20depend%20on%20interest%20rates.%20If%20you%20have%20any%20debt%20actively%20accruing%20large%20amounts%20of%20interest%2C%20those%20should%20always%20be%20the%20first%20things%20you%20address.%20Getting%20ahead%20of%20a%2025%25%20interest%20rate%20will%20always%20be%20your%20best%20bet%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20saving%20money%2C%20both%20now%20and%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20you%20didn't%20mention%20paying%20off%20any%20debt%20in%20your%20letter%2C%20though%2C%20I%20also%20asked%20Rush%20the%20best%20way%20for%20you%20to%20tailor%20your%20investment%20strategy%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20this%20financial%20gift.%20Rush%20says%20it%20all%20comes%20down%20to%20time%20and%20individual%20risk%20tolerance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20wait%20at%20least%20two%20or%20more%20years%20to%20access%20a%20portion%20of%20this%20money%2C%20investing%20is%20a%20great%20option%20%E2%80%94%20although%20Rush%20reiterated%20that%20investing%20always%20comes%20with%20a%20level%20of%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHiring%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-online-financial-advisors%5C%22%3Efinancial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20you%20navigate%20your%20risk%20exposure%20and%20find%20the%20best%20investments%20for%20you%20will%20give%20you%20both%20a%20sense%20of%20direction%20and%20peace%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%20you%20choose%20to%20invest%20your%20money%2C%20I%20hope%20you%20set%20aside%20a%20solid%20chunk%20for%20travel.%20Not%20to%20get%20too%20clich%C3%A9%2C%20but%20the%20time%20you%20enjoy%20wasting%20is%20not%20wasted.%20You%20can%20also%20apply%20this%20wisdom%20to%20money.%20Every%20time%20we%20spend%20our%20money%2C%20we%20are%20buying%20something.%20Whether%20that%20thing%20is%20tangible%2C%20like%20a%20car%20or%20a%20new%20pair%20of%20jeans%2C%20or%20intangible%2C%20like%20the%20experience%20of%20travel%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20see%20our%20tangible%20purchases%20as%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalk%20to%20me%20after%20a%20solid%20Target%20run%2C%20and%20I%20will%20give%20you%20a%20TED%20Talk%20on%20the%20importance%2C%20nay%2C%20the%20necessity%20of%20every%20single%20item%20in%20my%20bag.%20Worst%20case%2C%20as%20I%20often%20say%2C%20I%20can%20resell%20my%20newfound%20junk%20on%20Facebook%20Marketplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20we%20purchase%20things%20that%20we%20can't%20hold%20in%20our%20hands%2C%20point%20to%20in%20our%20driveways%2C%20or%20pull%20up%20in%20our%20portfolios%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20driving%20down%20the%20interstate%20with%20an%20open%20bag%20of%20cash%20in%20the%20back%20seat.%20Money%20just%20floating%20out%20the%20window%20in%20our%20wake%2C%20gone%20with%20nothing%20to%20show%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20having%20anything%20to%20show%20for%20your%20money%2C%20however%2C%20does%20not%20equate%20to%20frivolous%20spending.%20You%20still%20made%20a%20purchase.%20You%20bought%20standing%20at%20the%20top%20of%20a%20mountain%2C%20staring%20into%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20Mona%20Lisa%2C%20or%20witnessing%20the%20great%20wildebeest%20migration%20in%20Tanzania.%20These%20are%20once-in-a-lifetime%20experiences%20that%2C%20despite%20their%20price%20tag%2C%20are%20absolutely%20priceless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20joy%20of%20travel%2C%20however%2C%20there%20are%20also%20financially%20strategic%20ways%20to%20maximize%20the%20money%20you%20spend%20on%20seeing%20the%20world.%20With%20the%20right%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-travel-rewards-credit-cards%5C%22%3Etravel%20rewards%20credit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20can%20earn%20points%20that%20can%20go%20towards%20your%20next%20big%20trip.%20Some%20travel%20cards%20have%20big%20sign-on%20bonuses.%20If%20you%20spend%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20a%20short%20timeframe%2C%20you%20automatically%20earn%20a%20ton%20of%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20pay%20off%20bills%20with%20a%20portion%20of%20your%20inheritance%2C%20use%20your%20travel%20card%20to%20do%20it%20and%20earn%20those%20sign-on%20bonuses.%20This%20will%20allow%20you%20to%20pay%20for%20your%20flights%20with%20money%20you%20had%20to%20spend%20anyway.%20Then%2C%20once%20you've%20reached%20your%20destination%2C%20use%20your%20card%20for%20all%20your%20purchases%20and%20allow%20your%20travel%20now%20to%20pay%20for%20your%20travel%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20as%20you%20move%20forward%20with%20this%20inheritance%20is%20that%20while%20%2425%2C000%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20it's%20not%20enough%20to%20quit%20your%20job%20and%20retire%20to%20Fiji.%20So%2C%20don't%20put%20that%20kind%20of%20expectation%20on%20it.%20Instead%2C%20treat%20it%20like%20you%20landed%20on%20Free%20Parking%20in%20Monopoly%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pleasant%20surprise%20that%20you%20didn't%20have%20to%20work%20to%20earn%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20don't%20need%20to%20stress%20over%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20to%20say%20you%20shouldn't%20use%20your%20money%20to%20make%20more%20money.%20That's%20always%20a%20good%20idea.%20But%20make%20sure%20you%20enjoy%20some%20of%20your%20inheritance%20without%20trying%20to%20be%20practical%20over%20every%20cent.%20As%20Rush%20said%2C%20financial%20goals%2C%20life%20goals%2C%20and%20long-term%20plans%20are%20all%20subjective.%20The%20best%20balance%20between%20spending%20and%20saving%20is%20the%20balance%20that%20is%20right%20for%20your%20individual%20values%2C%20dreams%2C%20and%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWishing%20you%20safe%20and%20spectacular%20travels%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELooking%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20your%20savings%2C%20debt%2C%20or%20another%20financial%20challenge%20is%20affecting%20your%20relationships%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-find-financial-advisor%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fid