f%20behind-the-scenes%20drama.%20Abhishek%20and%20Aishwarya%2C%20who%20share%20a%20daughter%2C%20Aaradhya%2C%20are%20both%20focused%20on%20their%20careers%2C%20with%20Abhishek%20working%20on%20King%20and%20Aishwarya%20recently%20appearing%20in%20Ponniyin%20Selvan%3A%20II.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-jaya-bachchan-praises-aishwarya-rai-bachchans-awareness-of-family-friends%2Farticleshow%2F112117472.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Survey%20Shows%20Which%20Airplane%20Seats%20Are%20Most%20Popular%20Among%20Travellers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20the%20best%20airline%20seats%20might%20seem%20obvious%2C%20seating%20preferences%20often%20vary%20among%20passengers.%20To%20assist%20flyers%2C%20travel%20site%20Upgrade%20Points%20surveyed%20US%20travellers%20to%20determine%20their%20seat%20preferences%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F07%2F30%2Flifestyle%2Fsurvey-names-most-coveted-airline-seats%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20window%20seats%20to%20exit%20rows%2C%20our%20aeroplane%20seat%20survey%20has%20revealed%20the%20preferences%20and%20pet%20peeves%20of%20flyers%20across%20the%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20experts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20identify%20the%20preferred%20seats%2C%20the%20flight%20experts%20polled%203%2C142%20U.S.%20travellers%20over%20a%20week%20from%20June%2014%20to%20June%2020.%20Participants%20were%20shown%20a%20Boeing%20737-800%20seat%20map%20and%20asked%20to%20select%20their%20most%20desired%20seat%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20revealed%20that%20seat%201A%20-%20a%20first-class%20bulkhead%20window%20seat%20-%20was%20the%20top%20choice%20among%20participants.%20This%20was%20perhaps%20unsurprising%20given%20that%20this%20spot%20offers%20%26quot%3Bample%20legroom%2C%20easy%20restroom%20access%2C%20a%20window%20view%2C%20and%20the%20perk%20of%20being%20one%20of%20the%20first%20on%20and%20off%20the%20plane%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Upgraded%20Points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClose%20behind%20were%20seats%207A%20and%207F%20in%20coach%20class%2C%20which%20also%20offer%20plenty%20of%20legroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParents%20with%20small%20kids%20often%20favour%20the%20bulkhead%20seats%20in%20row%207%2C%20as%20they%20provide%20extra%20space%20for%20movement%20and%20easier%20access%20to%20overhead%20bins%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UP%20experts%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20being%20at%20the%20front%20of%20a%20section%2C%20bulkhead%20seats%20in%20row%207%20often%20experience%20less%20foot%20traffic%2C%20providing%20a%20slightly%20calmer%20environment%20for%20passengers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20seat%201F%20(first-class%20window%20seat)%20ranked%20fourth%2C%20followed%20by%207C%20(an%20economy%20aisle%20seat)%20in%20fifth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeats%204F%20and%2020A%20(exit%20row%20window%20seats)%20came%20in%20at%20sixth%20and%20seventh%20places%2C%20respectively%2C%20which%20UP%20attributed%20to%20the%20added%20legroom%20and%20the%20tendency%20for%20exit%20rows%20to%20have%20more%20empty%20seats%2C%20offering%20more%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%2041%25%20of%20respondents%20were%20%26quot%3Bwilling%20to%20accept%20the%20added%20responsibility%20of%20sitting%20in%20an%20exit%20row%20for%20the%20extra%20legroom%20and%20the%20peace%20of%20mind%20from%20being%20near%20a%20quick%20exit%20in%20case%20of%20an%20emergency%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20top%2015%20most%20preferred%20seats%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E1A%20-%20Window%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E7F%20-%20Window%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E7A%20-%20Window%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E1F%20-%20Window%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E7C%20-%20Aisle%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E4F%20-%20Window%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E20A%20-%20Window%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E1B%20-%20Aisle%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E4A%20-%20Window%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E20F%20-%20Window%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E7D%20-%20Aisle%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E10A%20-%20Window%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E12F%20-%20Window%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E2B%20-%20Aisle%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E8F%20-%20Window%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E66.6%25%20of%20respondents%20preferred%20a%20window%20seat%2C%20while%2031.7%25%20favoured%20an%20aisle%20seat.%20Only%201.7%25%20chose%20the%20middle%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20many%20experts%20agree%20that%20the%20middle%20seat%20is%20the%20safest%20in%20the%20event%20of%20an%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20preferred%20seats%20are%20located%20in%20bulkhead%20or%20exit%20rows.%20The%20survey%20also%20ranked%20seat%20preferences%20by%20state%2C%20revealing%20that%20New%20Yorkers%20prefer%20seat%204A%2C%20a%20window%20seat%20in%20the%20exit%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20found%20that%2060%25%20of%20people%20would%20pay%20to%20choose%20their%20seat%20in%20advance%2C%20with%20US%20passengers%20willing%20to%20spend%20an%20average%20of%20%2433.59%20for%20their%20preferred%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelta%20was%20the%20favourite%20among%20airlines%2C%20with%2033.6%25%20of%20flyers%20rating%20their%20seats%20as%20superior.%20American%20Airlines%20and%20United%20Airlines%20tied%20for%20second%20place%2C%20with%2015.9%25%20of%20respondents%20declaring%20their%20seats%20as%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpirit%20Airlines%20and%20Sun%20Country%20Airlines%20received%20the%20lowest%20ratings%2C%20with%20only%200.3%25%20of%20travellers%20preferring%20their%20accommodations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722768600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fst1o8mqo_airplane-generic-bloomberg_625x300_27_April