20collection%20has%20grown%20to%20an%20impressive%20300%20varieties.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20mastered%20the%20nuances%20of%20portulaca%20care%20by%20focusing%20on%20essentials%20like%20direct%20sunlight%2C%20minimal%20watering%2C%20regular%20pruning%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20organic%20fertilisers%20like%20cow%20dung.%20Besides%2C%20portulacas%20are%20known%20for%20their%20vibrant%20blooms%20and%20minimal%20care%20requirements.%20This%20fits%20perfectly%20into%20her%20busy%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20challenges%20in%20portulaca%20farming%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20rainy%20season%2C%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20a%20few%20varieties%20like%20Jumbo.%20I%20repot%20these%20plants%20and%20maintain%20new%20cuttings%20so%20that%20their%20roots%20do%20not%20rot%20in%20the%20excess%20rain%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20portulaca%20farming%2C%20she%20manages%20to%20get%2050-100%20orders%20in%20a%20day.%20With%20this%2C%20she%20says%20to%20generate%20an%20additional%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20As%20her%20business%20grows%2C%20Parvathy%20dreams%20of%20balancing%20her%20work%20and%20passion%20while%20expanding%20her%20venture.%20She%20also%20encourages%20others%20to%20opt%20for%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyone%20in%20need%20of%20additional%20income%20can%20do%20this%20as%20a%20business%20also.%20The%20key%20is%20to%20grow%20low-maintenance%20but%20high%20demand%20plants%20like%20portulaca%20and%20find%20a%20trustworthy%20team%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20work%20in%20your%20absence%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajani%20Mohanan%2C%20who%20has%20seen%20Parvathy%20toil%20hard%20while%20managing%20both%20the%20office%20and%20the%20farm%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20started%20this%20business%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20when%20she%20was%20just%20a%20college%20student.%20This%20has%20become%20an%20extra%20source%20of%20income%20for