ebetterindia.com%2F359012%2Fmanu-bhaker-paris-olympics-shooting-bronze-medal-pistol-first-indian-woman-history-sarabjot-singh-haryana%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Fought%20Early%20Marriage%20For%20My%20Dreams%E2%80%99%3A%20UP%20Girl%20Uses%20Unique%20Art%20to%20Help%2020%20Others%20Find%20Freedom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20market%20in%20Risia%20block%2C%20Bahraich%20district%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20bustling%20with%20activity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20big%20market%20for%20the%20entire%20block%2C%20there%20are%20several%20shops%20lining%20the%20narrow%20winding%20streets.%20While%20some%20sell%20groceries%2C%20vegetables%2C%20sweetmeats%20and%20readymade%20clothes%2C%20others%20offer%20tailoring%20and%20hair%20cutting%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESqueezed%20among%20them%20is%20a%20small%20shop%20run%20by%20Rachna%20Kumari%2C%20a%20petite%20and%20soft-spoken%20young%20woman%20selling%20unique%20wheat%20stalk%20paintings%20handmade%20by%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20surprisingly%2C%20this%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318714%2Ftamil-nadu-engineer-turns-artist-paints-with-sunlight-vignesh%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20unconventional%20entrepreneurial%20choice%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20made%20the%2023-year-old%20the%20cynosure%20of%20all%20eyes%20for%20more%20reasons%20than%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201512px)%20100vw%2C%201512px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rachna%20with%20one%20of%20her%20creations.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG_0730_11zon-1722256363.jpg%201512w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t