0of%20her%20paintings%2C%2050%20of%20which%20were%20bought%20since%20she%20opened%20her%20shop%20in%20April%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20achieved%20this%20admirable%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20opportunities%20make%20dreams%20come%20true%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202019%2C%20Rachna%20had%20almost%20given%20up%20on%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20became%20depressed%20after%20dropping%20out.%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20have%20to%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20days%20doing%20household%20chores.%20As%20the%20eldest%20of%20five%20siblings%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20me%20to%20get%20married%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Rachna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20the%20Aga%20Khan%20Foundation%20(AKF)%20came%20into%20the%20picture%20with%20Project%20Lehar.%20Started%20to%20provide%20vocational%20training%2C%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20life%20skills%20courses%20to%20marginalised%20young%20women%2C%20Project%20Lehar%2C%20run%20by%20AKF%20in%20partnership%20with%20The%20King%E2%80%99s%20Trust%20International%2C%20empowers%20girls%20and%20young%20women%20from%20disadvantaged%20backgrounds%20to%20rediscover%20and%20realise%20their%20potential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Project%20Lehar%20team%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290617%2Fsonal-shukla-educated-girls-mumbai-slums-feminist-icon-women-movement-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereaching%20out%20to%20help%20school%20dropouts%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Risia%20block%20restart%20their%20education.%20This%20was%20a%20godsend%20opportunity%20for%20Rachna%20to%20not%20just%20resume%20her%20studies%20but%20also%20to%20convince%20her%20parents%20to%20drop%20her%20marriage%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20was%20admitted%20into%20college%20through%20Project%20Lehar%2C%20she%20was%20also%20counseled%20on%20entrepreneurial%20and%20career%20prospects.%20One%20such%20session%20on%20wheat%20stalk%20painting%20was%20to%20change%20her%20life%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWheat%20stalk%20painting%2C%20a%20traditional%20art%20form%20of%20Bahraich%2C%20is%20a%20laborious%20and%20time%20consuming%20process.%20It%20is%20created%20by%20cutting%20wheat%20stalks%20into%20fine%20sections%20to%20craft%20intricate%20designs%20on%20cloth%20using%20sharp-edged%20blades%20and%20razors.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Some%20of%20Rachna's%20beautiful%20paintings%20made%20from%20wheat%20stalk.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358949%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESome%20of%20Rachna%E2%80%99s%20beautiful%20paintings%20made%20from%20wheat%20stalk.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20class%2010%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20study%20further%20because%20the%20government%20inter%20college%20was%20very%20far%20away%20from%20my%20house.%20My%20family%20income%20was%20not%20enough%20to%20enroll%20me%20in%20a%20private%20college%20nearby%20and%20they%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20me%20to%20study%20any%20more.%20But%20now%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344353%2Fwomen-in-finance-how-to-invest-stock-market-mutual-funds-monika-halan-mrin-agarwal-rachana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20am%20economically%20independent%20and%20am%20paying%20for%20my%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20BA%20third-year%20student%20proudly.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Rachna%20is%20not%20resting%20on%20her%20laurels.%20Her%20shop%20also%20doubles%20up%20as%20a%20training%20centre%20where%20other%20girls%20from%20marginalised%20backgrounds%20like%20her%20who%20want%20to%20stand%20on%20their%20feet%20get%20a%20second%20chance%20to%20change%20their%20lives%20like%20she%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20trains%20them%20six%20days%20a%20week%20in%20two%20batches.%20The%20one-month%20basic%20training%20course%20in%20wheat%20stalk%20painting%20costs%20Rs%20500%20per%20girl.%20Currently%2C%20she%20has%2020%20students%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2012%20and%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20teaching%20these%20enthusiastic%20young%20girls%20is%20a%20joyful%20experience%2C%20what%20gives%20Rachna%20immense%20pride%20is%20being%20chosen%20as%20a%20wheat%20stalk%20painting%20trainer%20in%20February%202024%20by%20the%20foundation.%20After%20being%20a%20trainee%20under%20this%20project%20to%20now%20becoming%20its%20paid%20trainer%2C%20Rachna%E2%80%99s%20life%20has%20come%20full%20circle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPaving%20a%20path%20for%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20Rachna%20almost%208-10%20hours%20to%20make%20one%20painting.%20The%20price%20of%20each%20framed%20wheat%20stalk%20painting%20ranges%20from%20Rs%201%2C000-3%2C000%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20intricacy%20of%20work%20and%20its%20