had%20eight%20subjects%20at%20that%20time%2C%20they%20completed%20their%20first%20revision%20in%20two%20months.%20They%20referred%20to%20The%20Institute%20of%20Chartered%20Accountants%20of%20India%20(ICAI)%20modules%20and%20past%20papers%2C%20and%20took%20some%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20revision%20included%20trying%20to%20solve%20past%20papers%2C%20which%20gave%20them%20an%20idea%20about%20which%20areas%20needed%20more%20focus.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20targeted%2010%20days%20for%20two%20subjects%20in%20this%20revision%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sachin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%2C%20they%20attempted%20some%20mock%20test%20papers%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20March.%20The%20results%20were%20shocking%2C%20says%20Sachin.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20failed%20in%20a%20few%20papers.%20Even%20in%20other%20subjects%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20result%20we%20wanted.%20We%20were%20shattered%20to%20see%20the%20result%20after%20all%20our%20hard%20work.%20This%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20enough%20to%20secure%20a%20rank%2C%20which%20was%20our%20aim%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin%20and%20Nandini%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20it%20lightly.%20They%20doubled%20their%20efforts%20and%20spoke%20to%20professors%20about%20what%20was%20lacking.%20The%20professors%20helped%20them%20with%20language%2C%20format%2C%20templates%2C%20and%20paper%20presentations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20also%20helped%20was%20their%20companionship.%20Nandini%20says%20it%20kept%20distractions%20at%20bay%20and%20made%20studying%20an%20enjoyable%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20bored%20when%20you%20study%20together.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20been%20study%20buddies%20since%20Class%202.%20We%20helped%20each%20other%20as%20we%20had%20complementary%20skill%20sets.%20We%20would%20teach%20each%20other%20the%20subjects%20we%20were%20strong%20in.%20Sachin%20also%20served%20as%20a%20benchmark%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nandini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%2